Package: didTEnets
Type: Package
Title: Transfer Entropy-Informed Difference-in-Differences for Network Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-12-23
Authors@R: person("Avishek", "Bhandari", 
                  email = "bavisek@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Implements the Transfer Entropy-informed Difference-in-Differences (TE-DiD) 
    framework for policy evaluation in interconnected systems. The package provides tools 
    for network-based contagion analysis, transfer entropy calculation, and robust causal 
    inference using difference-in-differences methodology. Key features include financial 
    network analysis, crisis contagion measurement, policy impact assessment, and 
    comprehensive visualization tools for network evolution across different time periods.
